.sp
.nf
.ft C
{\(aq<package_name>\(aq: \(aq<version>\(aq}
.ft P
.fi
.sp
External dependencies:
.sp
.nf
.ft C
Virtual package resolution requires aptitude.
Without aptitude virtual packages will be reported as not installed.
.ft P
.fi
.sp
