salt \(aq*\(aq pkg.install <package name>
.UNINDENT
.TP
.B refresh
Whether or not to clean the yum database before executing.
.TP
.B skip_verify
Skip the GPG verification check (e.g., \fB\-\-nogpgcheck\fP)
.TP
.B version
Install a specific version of the package, e.g. 1.0.9. Ignored
if "pkgs" or "sources" is passed.
.UNINDENT
.sp
Repository Options:
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B fromrepo
